{"ID":"20250903151229-qqep7nn","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250903151229-qqep7nn","title":"Knockknock","type":"doc","updated":"20260320102737"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250903151252-mjsqh1m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250903151252-mjsqh1m","updated":"20250903151326"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"敲两下解锁后备箱：8295 只负责将尾门开关下发给 32G -\u003e LHZCU，敲尾门 2 下后 EWS 将信号传递给 LHZCU，由 LHZCU 负责判断前置条件，若满足则 LHZCU 下发解锁尾门信号给 RZCU\n敲三下点亮 ISC：8295 负责记忆开关逻辑（跟车记忆），敲尾门 3 下后 EWS 将信号传递给 LHZCU -\u003e ICB 32G -\u003e ICB 8295，8295 负责判断前置条件，前置条件如下：\n敲击3次播放ISC向后表达使能开关开启（已签署ISC《用户须知》）\n车机上电\n挂P档\n非洗车模式\n若前置条件满足，8295 调用 32G DLP 播放 ISC 灯光表达\n注：进入 knock-knock 菜单、打开 ISC 开关时需要判断 快捷表达 中 ISC 数量"}]},{"ID":"20250903155307-wlatrno","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250903155307-wlatrno","updated":"20260320102737"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20250903155307-zylp8w7.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]}